R. RUTHENBURG, Suing for Himself, etc., v. THE LOUISVILLE TRUST COMPANY and Chemical Bank & Trust Company. No. 11125. United States Court of Appeals Sixth Circuit. April 6, 1950. R. Ruthenburg, Louisville, Ky., and W. C. Edrington, Louisville, Ky., for appellants. Ogden, Galphin & Abell, Louisville, Ky., and Blakey Helm, Louisville, Ky., for ap-pellees.

Before HICKS, Chief Judge, and McAL-LISTER, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellant, it is ordered that this appeal be and the same is hereby dismissed.
